item.title: CVE-2023-35900|2024-10-21T14:09:24.300Z -- ibm -- robotic%20process%20automation
item.description: IBM Robotic Process Automation for Cloud Pak 21.0.0 through 21.0.7.4 and 23.0.0 through 23.0.5 is vulnerable to disclosing server version information which may be used to determine software vulnerabilities at the operating system level. IBM X-Force ID: 259368.
